<section id="why-do-they-correspond" class="level2" data-number="2.4">
<h2 data-number="2.4" class="anchored" data-anchor-id="why-do-they-correspond"><span class="header-section-number">2.4</span> Why do they correspond?</h2>
<p>The individual bulbs in the mandelbrot set correspond to regions of stability. They also correspond to parameters of <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?c"> where a specific period cycle is attracting. For example, the largest bulb at the centre of the set corresponds to fixed points.</p>



